+      "character": "Brian",
+      "startTime": 48.76,
+      "finishTime": 54.62,
+      "dialogue": {
+        "text": "Exactly. And we could encourage peer-to-peer learning where the developers share experiences and solutions.",
+        "align": "right"
+      }
+    },
+    {
+      "character": "Brian",
+      "startTime": 54.9,
+      "finishTime": 57.4,
+      "dialogue": {
+        "text": "It might promote a more collaborative environment.",
+        "align": "right"
+      }
+    },
+    {
+      "character": "Alice",
+      "startTime": 57.4,
+      "finishTime": 62.8,
+      "dialogue": {
+        "text": "That sounds great. The developers should also have a chance to ask questions and discuss common challenges.",
+        "align": "left"
+      }
+    },
+    {
+      "character": "Alice",
+      "startTime": 63.3,
+      "finishTime": 66.44,
+      "dialogue": {
+        "text": "If we make the training more interactive, it could lead to better learning outcomes.",
